  - Span: 80 km between amplifiers
  - Protection: Diverse routing, automatic restoration

Wireless Mesh:
  - Standard: IEEE 802.11ay (WiGig)
  - Frequency: 60 GHz
  - Data Rate: 40 Gbps per link
  - Range: 300 meters
  - Self-organization: Fully autonomous mesh formation
